<!-- 
    The view.ejs file provides a selection of
    different view buttons that the user can  
    choose to view different parts/entities in 
    the database. Each view buttonallows the user 
    to see the entity type associated with that 
    button in the Patient Care Manager database.
    There are five view: Patients, Treatments, 
    Providers, Departments, and Statistics. An 
    "Exit" option is provided to bring the user 
    back to the home page.
    ...
